*.log

### ==============================
### Local & sensitive configs
### ==============================
# local.properties contains SDK path — machine-specific, never commit
local.properties

# Keystore / signing (NEVER commit private keys)
*.jks
*.keystore
keystore.properties
release-keystore.properties

